# init(_:)

**Initializer**

Convert this `UnownedJob/Priority` to a [doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/TaskPriority].

## Declaration

```swift
init?(_ p: JobPriority)
```

## Discussion

Most values are directly interchangeable, but this initializer reserves the right to fail for certain values.
